ECHOES Alert - Probe
===============================================================================

ECHOES Alert desc.

For more information, see:
  • ECHOES Technologies: http://www.echoes-tech.com

REQUIREMENTS
------------
In order to build ECHOES Alert - Probe you will need:

  • lijson = 7.5.0 (http://sourceforge.net/projects/libjson/)
Build it with following options: JSON_LIBRARY (edit JSONOptions.h and run "make SHARED=1; sudo make SHARED=1 install").
  • CUnit = 2.1 (http://cunit.sourceforge.net/)

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To build ECHOES Alert - Probe just run:

  $ ./configure
  $ make all
  # make install

BUGS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If you find a bug in ECHOES Alert - Probe, please create a Redmine entry here:

  https://redmine.gayuxweb.fr/projects/probe/issues/new

Attaching:

  • the version of ECHOES Alert - Probe
    ◦ if it is a development version, the branch of the git repository
  • a small test case, if none of the test units exhibit the behaviour
  • in case of a segmentation fault, a full stack trace with debugging
    symbols obtained through gdb is greatly appreaciated

